| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4909 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 20cbaa86-2b4b-5fc5-a707-73dd06415ad3"
